rComments: J'ai beaucoup aimé et appris dans ce cours. Elle est une enseignante et une chercheuse inspirante. Je conseil ce cours à tous ceux qui sont intéressé par la psychologie de la santé. Je referais ce cours n'importe quand.
The book was just god-awful. The teacher is really nice but her exams are really tough. Wouldn't take this course again, nor would I recommend it to someone else.

The teacher is decent. She's nice and she's helpful but a lot of her material is pretty random and you pretty much have to memorize everything even if she insists on the comprehension aspect of the material. Only take this class if mandatory.
She makes the class very interesting. Althought its alot of information to learn, she makes it easy to learn by giving concrete examples. Her feedback on exams is very useful.
Excellent teacher!!! Makes the class participate and uses movies, cases and special guests to make the class more interesting. I would recommend her to anyone.
